of learning mathematics.

00:01:32.990 --> 00:01:37.043
And in a lot of ways, this is how
you would master a lot of things in life.

00:01:37.067 --> 00:01:39.366
It's the way you would
learn a martial art.

00:01:39.390 --> 00:01:42.556
In a martial art, you would
practice the white belt skills

00:01:42.580 --> 00:01:43.993
as long as necessary,

00:01:44.017 --> 00:01:45.568
and only when you've mastered it

00:01:45.592 --> 00:01:47.727
you would move on to become a yellow belt.

00:01:47.751 --> 00:01:49.822
It's the way you learn
a musical instrument:

00:01:49.846 --> 00:01:52.140
you practice the basic piece
over and over again,

00:01:52.164 --> 00:01:53.752
and only when you've mastered it,

00:01:53.776 --> 00:01:55.447
you go on to the more advanced one.

00:01:55.471 --> 00:01:56.811
But what we point out --

00:01:56.835 --> 00:02:01.320
